channel.title: JDK 6 ! Someone help quickly?
channel.description:
Okay...so i'm using the ultimate server guide, and i am stuck on downloading JDK 6. I press JDK 6 with Java EE. Then i press accept. And there are buttons saying to dowload it with "sun download manager". Now under that button there are these things, (i have windows) so i chose "Windows Platform - Java EE SDK 5 Update 2". And the download is really slow....
AM I doing the right thing so far? COuld someone help me and make sure i'm on the right track. Does it usually take 20 minutes to download JDK 6?

Java EE means “Enterprise edition”. It has features intended to be used only on business class servers that would kick your computers ass. You want to get Java SE. And yes, it will take a long time to download, under most conditions.
